vent * Required Date of the event - must be mm/dd/yyyy format * Required   Date Format: MM slash DD slash YYYY   Start Time of the Event * Required    :  HH     MM    AM/PM  AM  PM    End Time of the Event * Required    :  HH     MM    AM/PM  AM  PM    Day and time alternative * Required We will do everything to reserve the Oasis at your preferred date and time. However, in case we are unable to do that, what are the other days and times that would work for your event? Estimated Number of Participants * Required Equipment and miscellaneous * Required Select which equipment you require as well as other tools/amenities that you would like to add to your reservation. If you need something that is not listed, please indicate it in "other" below.   Computer and projector    Big screen    Oasis TV (instead of the big screen)    Loud speakers    Microphone (to be used as the only output source)    Microphone with an additional output source (e.g. for Karaoke or similar events when you want to hear the voice from the microphone AND the voice from the computer)    Photo Camera    Video Camera    Popcorn Machine only (no pre-made popcorn)    Fresh popcorn (pre-made) and popcorn machine    Coffee cart    Other (specify below)  Other If you selected "other" above, please indicate what other equipment or amenities you need with your reservation. Who will host the event? * Required Just me Me and someone else Someone else Name of the (co)host: If you indicated that someone else will host the event with or without you, please enter their name here.    First     Last   Name of another co-host (optional):    First     Last   Other comments and information Please tell us anything else that you think is important about your reservation. Phone This field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged.   Save and Continue Later           This iframe contains the logic required to handle Ajax powered Gravity Forms.    Contact    Back to main content           General Inquiries    Equipment Reservation    Oasis Reservation          Peer Tutoring Contact Information  Click here if you have questions about our Peer Tutoring in French, German, Spanish, or Italian.      General Inquiries to LCLC  If you have a general inquiry to LCLC or are not sure which category it fits, send us an email here.      Equipment Reservation  The LCLC has a wide variety of equipment for language instructors and TAs. Click here to reserve equipment for your classroom or event.      School of Literatures, Cultural Studies and Linguistics  The School of Literatures, Cultural Studies and Linguistics (LCSL) is home to six independent departments, three academic programs, and the Sandi Port Errant Language and Culture Learning Center.                 UIC Logo         Language  And Culture  Learning Center  College of  Liberal Arts  And  Sciences         Contact   Language and Culture Learning Center  703 South Morgan St., 301 GH Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996 2119  lclc@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube            UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  Â© 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings     